00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:19.620
Camellias.

00:02:19.620 --> 00:02:22.930
They're quite easy to grow. You just have to
remember to

00:02:22.930 --> 00:02:27.270
be easy on the feed, and grow them in a
cool condition during the wintertime.

